      <title>20250107-B2xx-— A selection of recent explorations/variations. Using a photo of ...</title>
      <link>https://www.instagram.com/p/DFDIBh1RsF6/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/655252732_18110643835768976_5368514162536986387_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_s1080x1080_sh2.08_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=101&amp;ig_cache_key=MzU0OTcxNjIwODcxMjc2NjcwNw%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjE0NDB4MTQ0MC5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=dsbNciYezKMQ7kNvwHtc469&amp;_nc_oc=AdqfpIIF5LQXYXeD0w9QZt6tlHt0FTVX0ftG6LbykD7Xoyk0B_oNkVqbKSjftiE7-x0&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=g479Dl8bGEjKpRz1OkaonA&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfyEuHBwCkDDQ64kfYXzPkPBVarz8MhuAFYs8FIIoMxhRw&amp;oe=69C9C41A" alt="Instagram billede fra @skwiot" /></p><p><strong>@skwiot</strong></p><p>20250107-B2xx-—<br/>
<br/>
A selection of recent explorations/variations. Using a photo of a Madonna &amp; Child statue (found at a flea market in Amsterdam), I’ve been attempting to see how far I can push the limits of image and still be recognizable. Additionally, it’s a new thread in an on/off again look at the influence of catholicism on me, and the grandeur and spectacle yet intimate experience of everything. <br/>
<br/>
Original artwork available for licensing. Not available as an NFT. Mock-up materials by @blkmarket.<br/>
<br/>
#abstractart #art #abstractartwork #compactdisc #cd #vinyl #lp #light #3d #halftone #doommetal #deephouse #ambient</p>]]></description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/655252732_18110643835768976_5368514162536986387_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_s1080x1080_sh2.08_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=101&amp;ig_cache_key=MzU0OTcxNjIwODcxMjc2NjcwNw%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjE0NDB4MTQ0MC5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=dsbNciYezKMQ7kNvwHtc469&amp;_nc_oc=AdqfpIIF5LQXYXeD0w9QZt6tlHt0FTVX0ftG6LbykD7Xoyk0B_oNkVqbKSjftiE7-x0&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=g479Dl8bGEjKpRz1OkaonA&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfyEuHBwCkDDQ64kfYXzPkPBVarz8MhuAFYs8FIIoMxhRw&amp;oe=69C9C41A" alt="Instagram billede fra @skwiot" /></p><p><strong>@skwiot</strong></p><p>20250107-B2xx-—<br/>
<br/>
A selection of recent explorations/variations. Using a photo of a Madonna &amp; Child statue (found at a flea market in Amsterdam), I’ve been attempting to see how far I can push the limits of image and still be recognizable. Additionally, it’s a new thread in an on/off again look at the influence of catholicism on me, and the grandeur and spectacle yet intimate experience of everything. <br/>
<br/>
Original artwork available for licensing. Not available as an NFT. Mock-up materials by @blkmarket.<br/>
